       <li>
          <%= image_tag 'wrench.svg', class: 'svg-img'%>
       <span>Submit a property for purchase and we'll work with you every step of the way.</span>
       </li>
       <li>
          <%= image_tag 'head.svg', class: 'svg-img'%>
        <span>We are available via chat, email, phone and in person.</span>
       </li>
       <li>
          <%= image_tag 'homefill.svg', class: 'svg-img'%>
        <span>No need to set up open houses. Selling to us is a breeze!</span>
        </li>
     </ul>
   </div> 
  </div>

  <div class="row align-center agents-mid">
    <div class="small-11 medium-6 medium-offset-1 small-centered columns agent-contents">
      <h2>Maximum Marketing</h2>
      <p>Out of our range? We also offer <color>professional photos </color>, an immersive <color>virtual reality tours</color>, <color> aerial videos </color>, and more, to show your home at it's best. Our team has over a decade of professional real estate experience and can help get your home sold, hassle-free!
      </p>
      <div class="homepage-matterurl">
        <iframe width="680" height="410" src="<%=@property.matterurl%>" frameborder="0" allow-fullscreen ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row align-center agents-intro">
   <div class="small-11 medium-6 medium-offset-1 small-centered columns agent-contents  ">
     <h2>Guaranteed Price</h2>
     <p> Unsure of what your listing is worth? Our propriatery algorithms are built by industry experts. </p>
     <ul class="row align-center">
       <li>
          <%= image_tag 'dollar-symbol.svg', class: 'svg-img'%>
       <span>Our in-house algorithms evaluate hundreds of characteristics about your home and location.</span>
       </li>
       <li>
          <%= image_tag 'checklist.svg', class: 'svg-img'%>
        <span>A comprehensive report gives you and your buyers total transparency and peace-of-mind.</span>
